          <strong>
            gorgias.com
          </strong>
           has not yet been verified. You can still send emails from this address but you may be more susceptible to deliverability issues. Please verify your domain to ensure the best possible performance.
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <span>
      To enable DKIM signing for the
       
      <strong>
        gorgias.com
      </strong>
       domain, please add the information below to your DNS records via your DNS registrar. Note that verification of these settings
       
      <strong>
        may take up to 72 hours after submission
      </strong>
      .
       
      <a
        href="https://docs.gorgias.com/en-US/spf-dkim-support-81757"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
